  <brief_title>Influence of Plasma Rich in Growth Factors (PRGF) on Healing of Medial Collateral Ligament (MCL) Tear</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of PRGF on Healing of MCL Tear - Randomized-Double-Blind-Placebo Control Trail</official_title>
  <sponsors>
